<BLOCKQUOTE>
<HR>
togam wrote:<BR>
<DIV>i&nbsp; have a&nbsp; simple&nbsp; solution&nbsp; <EM><STRONG>,&nbsp; but&nbsp; noone&nbsp; will like it .<BR></STRONG></EM>
<HR>
</DIV></BLOCKQUOTE></DIV>
<P>Firstly, your solution was far from simple in terms of implementation and game balance...</P>
<P>Secondly, your solution would piss off pretty much every soloer (although wasn't completely unexpected from one of the poorest soloing classes in the game)</P>
<P>Thirdly, it's completely and utterly ridiculous... what happens when the Enchanter pulls aggro... forget EVER having crowd control... what happens when a Cleric gets aggro, well there go the heals... it'd ruin the game completely... </P>
<P>at least you got half of that right....</P>
