lling your &quot;fun factor&quot;, which is underlying as a key point as to why they are hesitant. I'm missing 4 years of retuning, I want it done now.<br><br>Multitanking isn't a warrior only thing. Knights can pull it off with little problem. What I do want to see if some very specific meelee mods removed from knights and casters in general, in order to really balance out non caster classes. Copy/Paste has hit a wall <span><img src='/i/smilies/16x16_smiley-surprised.gif' width=16 height=16 border=0></span><br></span></div>
