			A more realistic fix is to make casters and half-casters as frail as they should be with the cost of spellcasting being balanced by the inadvisability of obtaining aggro.<br><br>Then force Knights into chosing AC/HP's melee focuses/abilities OR Mana and caster focuses/abilities - not 95% Warrior and 75% Cleric. But rather more like 80% Warrior and 25% Cleric with the option of raising either capability at the cost of lowering the other. Want to tank like Warirors, then cast just like them too. Want to 90% res, group heal, buff? Then tank like a Cleric.<br><div></div>	
